name: Kidney Function Test
description: A kidney function test measures the levels of various substances in the blood to determine how well your kidneys are working.

name: Blood Sugar Test
description: A blood sugar test measures the amount of sugar (glucose) in your blood.

name: Complete Blood Count (CBC)
description: A complete blood count (CBC) is a blood test used to evaluate your overall health and detect a wide range of disorders, including anemia, infection, and leukemia.

name: Lipid Profile
description: A lipid profile is a blood test that measures the amount of cholesterol and fats called triglycerides in the blood.

name: Thyroid Function Test
description: A thyroid function test assesses the levels of thyroid hormones in your blood to check for thyroid gland abnormalities.
